notes:
This website intends to makes data related to the World Bank Group's finances available to you in a social and interactive format. The datasets currently available on this site are listed below. Click a dataset name to explore its data right in your browser. Each dataset provides simple tools to filter, visualize, discuss, share, and embed the data. It also provides easy access to the filters and charts others have created using the dataset.

Please note that the datasets are raw and may not have been audited yet â€“ our goal is to make raw data publicly available in open data format as soon as it is approved for public release through other channels. Please also refer to the datasets descriptions associated with each dataset for links to official versions (which generally contain slightly older but verified data).
